<strong>Relevanz:</strong> Erstes System über 330 GH/s NTLM (8 GPU-Cluster).
Gültig von der Industrie als Multi-GPU Referenz.
        </div>
<div class="reference">
<span class="reference-authors">Amazon Web Services</span> 2024.
          <span class="reference-title">Amazon EC2 P4d Proceedings - GPU Computing.</span>
<span class="reference-url"><a href="https://aws.amazon.com/ec2/instance-types/p4/" target="_blank">https://aws.amazon.com/ec2/e instance-Typen/p4/</a></span>
